  "description": "Voice 1: Additive at brightness 0.75, full harmonic series. Voice 2: Additive at brightness 0.18, only the fundamental and second harmonic — a ghost fundamental 18 dB below the main voice. HAMMER at +0.15 introduces subliminal spectral blend. Voice 2 is barely audible but creates a phantom sub-octave that is felt in the chest, not heard with the ears. The Ghost Harmonic trick applied through OUIE's duophonic architecture.",
